ireAid”，将于 1 月 30 日在洛杉矶 Intuit Dome 举行，所得款项将用于重建项目和帮助流离失所的家庭。目前尚未公布阵容。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jamie-lee-curtis-donates-1million-to-los-angeles-wildfire-relief-efforts-3828267"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>吉他中心还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guitar-center-offers-to-replace-instruments-lost-in-los-angeles-wildfires-3828262">宣布了一项新计划，将帮助受洛杉矶野火影响的音乐家</a>更换乐器或装备。</p></div></div><p>唱片学院首席执行官首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-2025-grammys-will-proceed-as-planned-confirms-recording-academy-ceo-3828582">，确认 2025 年格莱美颁奖典礼将按计划进行</a>。</p> ;
